{"tid":930703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★政府來年未必有太多盈餘　葉劉：唔建議派錢，建議公屋免租一個月","createTime":"2018-12-06T13:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T09:09:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":95,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5eed1c74fb992900aa1003d74038746bb6b13d6e","tid":930703,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"政府明年2月公布新一份財政預算案，新民黨今午(6日)與財政司司長陳茂波會面。該黨立法會議員葉劉淑儀會後指，預計來年度經濟發展有許多不明朗因素，港府未必有太大盈餘。被問到會否支持全民派錢，她表示<span style=\"color: red;\">該黨不建議派錢</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n津貼方面，他們建議放寬「為低收入的殘疾人士照顧者提供生活津貼試驗計劃」的入息上限、<span style=\"color: red;\">按年齡調高「生果金」</span>。至於住屋和交通，則<span style=\"color: red;\">建議公屋免租一個月</span>、引入劏房租金管制及租金津貼，以及檢視港鐵票價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181206/bkn-20181206201140287-1206_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181206%2Fbkn-20181206201140287-1206_00822_001.html&d=iEKOJ8xOQcv6zySBd85AnjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=3dc3a43d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181206/bkn-20181206201140287-1206_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f3006ffa7b2fd09bae8bb5e9a306988b08019d15","tid":930703,"uid":114097,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"又話大把淨<br />\n重可以起人工島㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee400fcf0cac95c818c9beeefc9d4f4cc76cf4d","tid":930703,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><del>派錢</del></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n按年齡調高「生果金」<br />\n<br />\n議公屋免租一個月"},{"pid":"4fa1e1abc7729ba2b9e39f846da05a6f8d0ba4a6","tid":930703,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},